-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-10/xander-co-ltd-april-sales-fall-12-32-table-6118-tt.html
XANDER CO LTD said unconsolidated sales
in April fell 12.32% to NT$634,842,000 from NT$724,017,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  4/2011           4/2010
Sales            634,842          724,017    
YOY%             -12.32%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           2,747,279        3,224,158   
YOY%             -14.79% 
=================================================================
 